    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 2nd level, your quick thinking and agility allow you to move and act quickly. You can use a bonus action on each of your turns in combat to take the Dash, Disengage, Hide, or Use an Object action.</p>\n<p>Additionally, if you have not moved on your turn, you can give yourself advantage on your next melee attack roll on the current turn as a bonus action. After you do so, you are immobilized until the end of the current turn.</p>",
